Shugaban gwamnati na Indiya zai halarci haikali mai girma a wurin da ake jayayya
NEW DELHI (AP) - Filimin Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci wani babban bikin wata na gaba don haikalin Hindu a wani wuri da ake jayayya a arewacin Indiya inda masu ƙarfi na Hindu suka rushe masallaci na ƙarni na 16 a shekara ta 1992, in ji ƙungiyar da ke kula da gina haikali.
An shirya bikin a ranar 5 ga Agusta, ranar da masu tsara ya ce tana da amfani ga Hindus amma wannan ya kuma nuna shekara ɗaya tun da Parlamentin India ya kawar da matsayin ɗan'uwansa na ƙasar Musulmi kaɗai, Jammu da Kashmir.
Wannan alamar ba ta yiwu ba ga masu goyon bayan da kuma ' yan hamayya na Ƙasar Hindu na Modi, Ko BJP, wanda saƙonsa ya yi shekaru da yawa ya haɗa da alkawarin kawar da ' yancin Kashmir da kuma gina haikali ga allahn Hindu Ram inda masallaci na zamanin Mughal ya dā ya tsaya, wuri a birnin Ayo yi a ƙasar Uttar Pradesh da masu bauta suke gaskata cewa shi ne wurin haihuwar Ram.
Domin har ila cutar coronavirus tana ƙaruwa a dukan ƙasar Indiya, wadda ta ba da rahoto na uku mafi girma a duniya, za a sanar da bikin a tashar telibijin gwamnati kuma adadin masu sa hannu da masu kallon za su ƙara, in ji Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Ƙungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, rukunin hindu da ya yi tarayya da BJP.
Haikalin zai zama "maƙasudin haɗin kai na jama'a, haɗin kai na ƙasa da haɗin kai da kuma ta da jinin Hindutva," ko kuma hanyar rayuwa ta Hindu, mai magana na ƙungiyar Vinod Bansal ya ce a wani jama'a a ranar Asabar.
An magance jayayya ta ƙarni da yawa game da wurin a shekara ta ƙarshe bayan nasara mai girma na zaɓi na BJP.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Mafi Girma ta ba da hukunci a kan ƙungiyar haikalin, ta ce za a ba Musulmi roƙo a wani wuri dabam.
