Babban banki na Biritaniya HSBC ya ƙi "ya kafa tarko" ga Huawei na ƙasar China a bincike na Amirka - RT Business News
Bankin ƙasashe da yawa da ke hedkwatar London HSBC ya yi amfani da yaɗa kwanan wata don ya ce ba haka ba ne, kamar yadda wasannin wasa na ƙasar China suka da'awa, "ya ƙirƙira tabbaci" a kan Huawei, wanda ya sa aka kama shugaban shugaban kuɗi na kamfani a Kanada.
A cikin wani saƙon da yanzu ba a samu a WeChat, mai ba da rance ya ce ayyukansa ba su sa a yi bincike a Amirka game da babban mai tanadin kayan sashen saka hannu a duniya ba, yayin da binciken Huawei don ƙarya da aka yi cewa ya karya hani na Amirka a Iran ya soma kafin saka hannu na banki a ƙarshen shekara ta 2016.
"HSBC ba ta da wani ƙiyayya ga Huawei kuma ba ta "ƙera" Huawei ba," bangkin ya ce a ranar Asabar, kuma ya daɗa cewa ba zai taɓa ɓata wani gaskiya game da masu amfaninsa ba.
"Don amsa tambayoyin DA US DOJ na [Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka] don bayani, HSBC Group kawai ta gabatar da ainihin gaskiyar.
HSBC ba ta "ƙirƙira" tabbaci ko kuma "ɓoye" gaskiya ba."
Ƙari ga haka, a rt.com da ƙasar Ingila ta hana Huawei daga dandalin 5G ya nuna cewa Amirka tana gaya wa Biritaniya sararin abubuwa na ƙasashe - George Galloway zuwa Boom Bust
An hana wannan saƙon a kan dakalin da labari cewa "ya karya dokoki" kuma ba a samu yanzu ba.
Wannan furcin ya zo ba da daɗewa ba bayan wasa da yawa na ƙasar China, har da jaridu da suke da haɗin kai da gwamnati, sun zargi HSBC cewa ta "yi ƙarya" da Washington don ta kafa tarko ga Huawei.
Wannan kamfani ya yi fiye da shekara ɗaya da rabi a wannan kamfani tun lokacin da aka kama mai kula da Huawei, Meng Wanzhou a watan Disamba na shekara ta 2018 a Kanada don umurnin da aka ba shi daga Amirka.
An yi wa Meng zargin ƙarya don ya yi amfani da wata kamfani don ya karya hani da aka yi wa Iran kuma an ce ya yi ƙarya ga banki game da nasaba tsakanin Huawei da kamfani na Iran Skycom.
Bisa ga sababbin tabbaci da Global Times ta ambata, HSBC ta san dangantakar kamfani na China da Skycom.
An ce bangkin ya zaɓi ya "ya yi ƙulla" da gwamnati ta Amirka don ya guje wa horo mai tsanani a shekara ta 2012, sa'ad da bangkin ya yarda da ɓarnar kuɗi da kuma laifi, har da hani a Iran.
A lokacin an umurce shi ya biya kusan dola biliyan 1.9 a horo kuma ya hana irin wannan laifi.
"Shaidar ta nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan dangantakar amma ta sayar da takardun kasuwanci na asiri na masu amfani da shi ga gefen Amirka don gwamnati ta Amirka ta yi watsi da laifi na banki na Biritaniya kuma ba ta hukunta ta ƙarƙashin Shari'ar Ɗa'a ta 2012," jaridar ta ce a ɗaya daga cikin talifofinta a batun.
A cikin gargaɗi da aka ɓoye, jaridar beijing ta daɗa cewa mai ba da rance, idan an tabbatar da cewa shi ne mai laifi na wannan "shiri," zai iya fuskantar "azaba mai tsanani" a ƙasar China, ɗaya cikin babban kasuwanci na HSBC.
Wannan ba lokaci na farko ba ne da aka yi wa wannan banki mai suna wuta a cikin makonni na baya.
Wata na baya, an yi wa HSBC zargin goyon bayan sabuwar doka ta kāriya ta ƙasa a Hong Kong, birni da kasuwancinta ya soma kuma wanda ya ɗauki fiye da rabi na kuɗinsa.
Bankin ya fuskanci sūka daga gefen biyu - daga Yakuwa, da Sakata na Amirka Mike Pompeo ya kira goyon bayan "kowtow na kamfani," da gabas, da gefen ƙasar China ya ce goyon bayansa "ya ɗan jinkiri."
Masu makaman wuta sun samu ƙarfi a wuta a Ƙasar Lassen
