Wuta ta Zinariya, da ta soma kudun Adin, tana da kashi 40% yayin da take ci gaba da barazanar gidaje da gona da kuma aiki na gona, dabbobi da katako, ma'aikatan Cal Fire sun ce a sabonta da safiyar Asabar.
Bayan sun ƙona kwanaki huɗu, wutar ta cinye acre 21,000, ta halaka gidaje bakwai kuma ta tura masu wuta biyu zuwa asibiti.
