SEATTLE - Bayan makonni da yawa da ake faɗa tsakanin masu hamayya da hukumomi a birnin Portland, a jihar Ore., mutane kusan 2,000 sun shiga birnin Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafiya a kan titi kuma suna faɗa da ' yan sanda.
' Yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, har da ɗaya da aka kai asibiti da ciwon ƙafa da ya jawo nishaɗi, kuma an kama masu hamayya 16 da daɗewa, ' yan sanda sun ce.
Da suke ɗauke da alamun kamar "Feds Go Home" da kuma yin ihu na "Ba a yin adalci, babu salama," masu hamayya sun tsaya a wurin da ake tsare matasa a nan gaba kuma suka ƙona gini a wurin.
