Farfesa Caroline Smith, mai kula da ƙananan
Masanan kimiyya sun tabbata cewa dutsen da suke komawa Mars ya fito ne daga duniya, in ji Smith, wanda shi ma yana cikin rukunin kimiyya na Mars a shekara ta 2020.
"Ƙananan ƙananan gas da aka kama a cikin wannan meteorite suna da daidai daidai da yanayin Mars, don haka mun san dutsenmu ya fito daga can."
