oOh! Media ta tara kuɗi a farkon wannan shekara don ta ba da ƙarin tabbaci na kuɗi yayin da cutar ta soma tsoro ga masu yin shelar.
Waɗanda suka sani sun ce kamfani suna tattauna hanyoyin da za su kawar da ƙaruwar ta wajen rage kira a wuraren da suke aiki ko kuma ta wurin cire ko rage kuɗin da ake bayarwa, wanda ake amfani da shi sa'ad da aka ɗauki alkawarin da farko.
Wani tushe ya nuna cewa wataƙila manyan kamfani sun tabbatar da kashi 85 na kuɗin da suke samu a kira.
Wasu ƙa'idodin suna da layi da ke sa su rage ƙaramin tabbaci idan adadin mutanen da ke wani yankin ya rage da wani kashi, amma ba a sani ko wannan yanayin yana cikin kowace ƙarin alkawarin da ake yi tsakanin kamfani da masu gidansu.
Ƙari ga haka, kamfani suna ba masu yin shelar kuɗi sosai don su cika wuraren da ake samu a kan tafiyar tafiyar da kuma ba su kuɗin da ya fi amfani.
Wasa da ke birnin Sydney CBD da kuma gefen gunduma da suke ɗauke da sanarwa shida suna ƙoƙari su cika dukan wuraren da ake samu.
Amma an kyautata wasu dandalin - kamar oOh! na wasa na mita 40 x 10 a Firgin Magana na Sydney -.
oOh! Media ta ƙi yin kalami, amma a taron da aka yi a birnin Macquarie a ƙasar Ostareliya a watan Mayu, ta nuna cewa an ajiye fiye da dola miliyan 20 don kuɗin kira.
JC Decaux ya ƙi ya yi kalami.
Wasan tashar jirgin sama da kuma mota suna samun kuɗi sosai don su yi wa kamfani na yin saka hannu a kan takarda.
In ji rahoton Ƙungiyar Media Association ta shekara ta 2019, kuɗin da ake samu daga mota, har da tashar jirgin sama, ya kai dala miliyan 169.4, kuma kuɗin da ake samu daga kayayyakin titi da waje na bas da jirgin ƙasa ya kai dala miliyan 266.5.
AN YI ƙarin aiki a filin jirgin sama na Sydney, Yarra Trams, Firgin Magana na Perth da sydney Buses. oOh! Media yana da tafiye - tafiye a wurare kamar su kujerun Qantas, a waje da tashar jirgin sama na Sydney, Firgin Magana na Adelaide, Fisan Firgin Magana na Darwin da kuma cikin tashar jirgin ƙasa a Sydney da Melbourne.
Ana sayar da jirgin sama na Melbourne da jirgin ƙasa na Sydney a lokacin cutar kuma ba a tsai da shawara ba.
Melbourne ita ce babban alkawarin tashar jirgin sama na biyu a Ostareliya kuma kafin coronavirus tana da tamani na miliyoyin mutane kowace shekara.
A cikakken sakamakon shekara a watan Fabrairu, oOh! Media ta ce ta samu $65.9 miliyan daga rukuninta na 'fly', wanda yawancinsa ya ƙunshi kuɗi daga Firgin Magana na Sydney.
