Amma Mechichi ba ɗaya ba ne cikin sunayen da rukunin siyasa da ke sarauta suka ba wa Sarki Kais Saied shawara.
A cikin wani furci bayan sanarwar ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai "yi aiki don ya kafa gwamnati da take cika fatawar dukan Tunisia."
An yaba wa Tunisia a matsayin labarin nasara mai ban sha'awa don canji na demokrasi bayan tawayen da aka yi a yankin Arab Spring a shekara ta 2011.
Amma shugabanninta sun yi ƙoƙari su cika fatan mutanen Tunisia kuma an yi wa tattalin arziki da ya riga ya raunana ta wajen rufe iyaka ƙasar domin cutar COVID-19.
Wannan cutar ta kashe kusan mutane 50 kuma ta ciwo fiye da mutane 1,400 a Tunisia.
Ban da zama mai hidima a gwamnati da ta bar, Mechichi ya zama mai shawarar Sarki Saied, yana kula da batutuwa na shari'a.
A dā shi shugaban ma'aikatan Ɗakin Sutura ne kuma ya yi hidima a Ƙasashen Al'amura na Ƙasashe.
